{"type":null,"faqId":33237,"title":"为什么上网速度比较慢？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">理论网速4G&gt;3G&gt;2G。首先观察下手机当前是在什么网络。其次，各运营商网速有差异。另外，手机上网跟当时手机所在环境有关系。所以请在同一网络制式、同一地点下进行对比。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">上网速度慢的原因：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.网页容量比较大，加载需要更多时间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.网络环境不好，如在一个很密闭的环境、高铁上等。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.访问的网站的服务器有异常。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">在省电模式下会产生上网慢的感受。在 设置-省电管理 中可以设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">可以使用测速软件 SPEEDTEST 做测试，但一定要选择同样的服务器。不同的服务器测试速度会差异较大。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">可以采取以下措施：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.先检查当时是否后台应用在上网。 </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.做对比测试。将该卡放入别的手机，或者用别人相应制式的卡放入自己的手机。如果卡的效果不佳，建议去营业厅换卡。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.可以将应用关闭重新打开，或者软件卸载重新安装。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4.关闭移动数据再打开。启动飞行模式，再关闭飞行模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5.进入 设置-无线和网络-更多-移动网络-接入点名称（APN），重置为默认APN。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">6.重启手机。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7939","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748539000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":71,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"上网,速度,慢","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}